      "content": "it's more than just the blueprints though. i was looking at the actual coordinates of the intersections. some of them align perfectly with certain ley lines or whatever people call them. it's like they were building on top of something that was already there. i noticed a specific triangle formed by three landmarks in london that mirrors a weird shape in the financial district in NY. do you think it's possible someone was using a specific geometric code to link these cities together? like a way to mark certain spots for something else?",
